Building a Python package
=========================

First, build xapian-core for static linking:

$ cd xapian-core
$ ./configure --enable-static --disable-shared --enable-pic [--enable-maintainer-mode] (when building from git)
$ make

Install the required Python packages:

$ pip install sphinx build

Then build the Python module:

$ cd xapian-bindings
$ XAPIAN_CONFIG=../xapian-core/xapian-config ./configure --with-python3 [--enable-maintainer-mode] (when building from git)
$ cd python3
$ make

Make sure that the module is usable:

$ python test_xapian_star.py

Finally, build the Python package:

$ python -m build --wheel

The package will be in in dist/.
